<br />
Free People: <br />
<br />
I mix the ring-bound ranger and the fortifications. I use the fortifications that make -X vitality so I can kill them after with my bows. Light Shining Faintly is there to heal my ring-bound men. And with Frodo, TT, I can easly remove those burdens. Bid at least 3 and go first. <br />
<br />
Shadow: <br />
<br />
A great southron deck that focus on wounding Frodo with assassin and Eastern Emyn Muil. I&#39;ve put many ambush guys to make more usefull the Army of Haradhrim to get Mumak and win more skirmish + making them fierce. With that, I can make Assassin even more usefull. <br />
